KW  - Intermediate targets
KW  - Monetary targeting
KW  - ECB
AB  - The purpose of the paper is to survey and discuss inflation targeting in the context of monetary policy rules. The paper provides a general conceptual discussion of monetary policy rules, attempts to clarify the essential characteristics of inflation targeting, compares inflation targeting to monetary targeting and nominal-GDP targeting, and draws some conclusions for the monetary policy of the European System of Central Banks.
